queries.sql: SELECT `dd`.`doc_controlno` as `dcon`, `dr`.`subject`, `o`.`shortname` AS `orig_office`, `po`.`shortname` AS `current_office`, `ddoctype`.`type_codes`, `ddoctype`.`type_descs`, `dd`.`sequence_no` AS `first_seqno`, `dd`.`date_rcv` AS `first_date_rcv`, `dd`.`time_rcv` AS `first_time_rcv`, `last_seq`.`sequence_no` AS `last_seqno`, `last_seq`.`status` AS `last_seq_status`, `last_seq`.`date_rcv` AS `last_seq_date_rcv`, `last_seq`.`time_rcv` AS `last_seq_time_rcv`, `last_seq`.`date_action` AS `last_seq_date_action`, `last_seq`.`time_action` AS `last_seq_time_action`, `last_seq`.`release_date` AS `last_seq_release_date`, `last_seq`.`release_time` AS `last_seq_release_time`, `last_seq`.`remarks` AS `last_seq_remarks`, `last_seq`.`remarks2` AS `last_seq_remarks2`, `prev_last_seq`.`sequence_no` AS `prev_last_seqno`, `prev_last_seq`.`status` AS `prev_last_seq_status`, `prev_last_seq`.`date_rcv` AS `prev_last_seq_date_rcv`, `prev_last_seq`.`time_rcv` AS `prev_last_seq_time_rcv`, `prev_last_seq`.`date_action` AS `prev_last_seq_date_action`, `prev_last_seq`.`time_action` AS `prev_last_seq_time_action`, `prev_last_seq`.`release_date` AS `prev_last_seq_release_date`, `prev_last_seq`.`release_time` AS `prev_last_seq_release_time`, `prev_last_seq`.`remarks` AS `prev_last_seq_remarks`, `prev_last_seq`.`remarks2` AS `prev_last_seq_remarks2` FROM `docdetails` `dd` LEFT JOIN ( SELECT docdetails.doc_controlno, docdetails.sequence_no, docdetails.office_destination, docdetails.date_rcv, docdetails.time_rcv, docdetails.date_action, docdetails.time_action, docdetails.release_date, docdetails.release_time, docdetails.status, docdetails.prev_sequence_no, docdetails.remarks, docdetails.remarks2 FROM docdetails JOIN ( SELECT doc_controlno, MAX(sequence_no) AS max_seq FROM docdetails GROUP BY doc_controlno ) max_tracker ON docdetails.doc_controlno = max_tracker.doc_controlno AND docdetails.sequence_no = max_tracker.max_seq ) last_seq ON `dd`.`doc_controlno` = `last_seq`.`doc_controlno` LEFT JOIN `docdetails` `prev_last_seq` ON `last_seq`.`doc_controlno` = `prev_last_seq`.`doc_controlno` AND `last_seq`.`prev_sequence_no` = `prev_last_seq`.`sequence_no` LEFT JOIN `docregistry` `dr` ON `dd`.`route_no` = `dr`.`route_no` LEFT JOIN `office` `o` ON `dr`.`officecode` = `o`.`officecode` LEFT JOIN `office` `po` ON `last_seq`.`office_destination` = `po`.`officecode` LEFT JOIN ( SELECT rd.route_no, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT dt.type_code ORDER BY dt.type_code SEPARATOR ', ') AS type_codes, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT dt.type_desc ORDER BY dt.type_desc SEPARATOR ', ') AS type_descs FROM registry_doctype rd JOIN doc_type dt ON rd.type_code = dt.type_code GROUP BY rd.route_no ) ddoctype ON `dr`.`route_no` = `ddoctype`.`route_no` WHERE `dd`.`sequence_no` = 1 AND `dd`.`status` != 'A' AND ( `dd`.`doc_controlno` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `dr`.`subject` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `o`.`shortname` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `po`.`shortname` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `ddoctype`.`type_descs` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' ) ORDER BY `dd`.`doc_controlno` ASC LIMIT 20

SELECT COUNT(*) AS `numrows` FROM `docdetails` `dd` LEFT JOIN ( SELECT docdetails.doc_controlno, docdetails.sequence_no, docdetails.office_destination, docdetails.date_rcv, docdetails.time_rcv, docdetails.date_action, docdetails.time_action, docdetails.release_date, docdetails.release_time, docdetails.status, docdetails.prev_sequence_no, docdetails.remarks, docdetails.remarks2 FROM docdetails JOIN ( SELECT doc_controlno, MAX(sequence_no) AS max_seq FROM docdetails GROUP BY doc_controlno ) max_tracker ON docdetails.doc_controlno = max_tracker.doc_controlno AND docdetails.sequence_no = max_tracker.max_seq ) last_seq ON `dd`.`doc_controlno` = `last_seq`.`doc_controlno` LEFT JOIN `docdetails` `prev_last_seq` ON `last_seq`.`doc_controlno` = `prev_last_seq`.`doc_controlno` AND `last_seq`.`prev_sequence_no` = `prev_last_seq`.`sequence_no` LEFT JOIN `docregistry` `dr` ON `dd`.`route_no` = `dr`.`route_no` LEFT JOIN `office` `o` ON `dr`.`officecode` = `o`.`officecode` LEFT JOIN `office` `po` ON `last_seq`.`office_destination` = `po`.`officecode` LEFT JOIN ( SELECT rd.route_no, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT dt.type_code ORDER BY dt.type_code SEPARATOR ', ') AS type_codes, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT dt.type_desc ORDER BY dt.type_desc SEPARATOR ', ') AS type_descs FROM registry_doctype rd JOIN doc_type dt ON rd.type_code = dt.type_code GROUP BY rd.route_no ) ddoctype ON `dr`.`route_no` = `ddoctype`.`route_no` WHERE `dd`.`sequence_no` = 1 AND `dd`.`status` != 'A' AND ( `dd`.`doc_controlno` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `dr`.`subject` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `o`.`shortname` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `po`.`shortname` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' OR `ddoctype`.`type_descs` LIKE '%6000%' ESCAPE '!' )
